+' Version 1.1 2/4/2018
+
+'**********************************************************************************************************
+'002 - benji - nfozzy physics scripting added:flipper polarity, tricks, rubber dampening, separated posts and rubber bands, assigned materials.
+'003 - Skitso - skitso style inserts, new flashers, new lut, new ball/scratches textures, fixed a DB issue where flashers didn't show under T2 hand plastics
+'004 - iaakki - reworked 2X and shoot again inserts. Reduced lamp timer from 5 to 8 to make fading slower without perf penalty.
+'**********************************************************************************************************
